{"tid":891113,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA RTX 20 傳壞卡災情！GDDR6 過熱逾 100℃ 疑成元凶","createTime":"2018-11-06T00:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T20:23:53.000Z","uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7e13a999bbce3f39d05d1ae26c7b5c69714fda41","tid":891113,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2200944/20181104_RTX20-1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2200944%2F20181104_RTX20-1_1024.jpg&h=c8e4243c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRTX 2080 Ti 及 RTX 2080 顯示卡傳出壞卡災情，NVIDIA 官方現階段否認有此事，但德國 gotIT! Tech Media 網站利用紅外綫測溫儀器，發現問題元凶是卡上的 Micron GDDR6 記憶體，運作時溫度超逾 100℃，超出了它 95℃ 運作溫度上限。RTX 2080 Ti 及 RTX 2080「炒價」最高分別逾 $13,000 及 $7,500，對於已購買的用家們，若不幸壞卡固然心痛！<br />\n<br />\n自上星期起，NVIDIA 官方及 Reddit 着名討論區，均有 RTX 2080 Ti 及 RTX 2080 用家帖文訴苦，指顯示卡開始出現「花畫面」、BSOD「藍畫面」死機，甚至完全「變磚」即開機時完全無畫面，無法被系統辨認出來。綜合各方消息，除了各 AIC (Add-In Card) 廠商生產的 RTX 2080 Ti、RTX 2080 產品，甚至 NVIDIA 官方 Founders Editon 原裝卡也一樣出現壞卡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA 淡化事件<br />\n<br />\nRTX 2080 Ti 及RTX 2080 核心晶片，均由當今最先進的 TSMC (台積電) 7nm 製程生產，最初被認為是晶片質素有瑕疵。但德國 gotIT! 網站找到新證據，他們利用紅外綫測溫儀器，實時監察 RTX 2080 Ti 及 RTX 2080 背面綫路溫度，證實卡上 Micron GDDR6 記憶體最高溫度超逾 100℃，超出了它 95℃ 運作溫度上限，推斷這是壞卡元凶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=eG%2BH%2BmnwJydb3jju8aYqiZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6b2fdf5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者近期測試過、拆過各大品牌的 RTX 2080 Ti、RTX 2080 及 RTX 2070 顯示卡，各 AIC 廠商產品的散熱器，其底部均能覆蓋核心晶片與 GDDR6 顆粒表面，並例必在「GDDR6 &harr; 散熱器」之間加上傳熱貼 (Thermal Pad)，藉此將熱力傳導至散熱器。NVIDIA 官方方面，現階段則淡化事件，認為壞卡只屬於個別事件，並不認為 RTX 20 系列壞卡情況較上代 GTX 10 系列明顯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2200944/20181104_RTX20-3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2200944%2F20181104_RTX20-3_600.jpg&h=f3b2e385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2200944/20181104_RTX20-4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2200944%2F20181104_RTX20-4_600.jpg&h=872a0a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉自 eZone : <a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2200944/NVIDIA%20RTX%2020%20%E5%82%B3%E5%A3%9E%E5%8D%A1%E7%81%BD%E6%83%85%EF%BC%81GDDR6%20%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E9%80%BE%20100%E2%84%83%20%E7%96%91%E6%88%90%E5%85%83%E5%87%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2200944%2FNVIDIA%2520RTX%252020%2520%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25A3%259E%25E5%258D%25A1%25E7%2581%25BD%25E6%2583%2585%25EF%25BC%2581GDDR6%2520%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%2580%25BE%2520100%25E2%2584%2583%2520%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2587%25B6&d=eG%2BH%2BmnwJydb3jju8aYqiZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0b536529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2200944/NVIDIA%20RTX%2020%20%E5%82%B3%E5%A3%9E%E5%8D%A1%E7%81%BD%E6%83%85%EF%BC%81GDDR6%20%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E9%80%BE%20100%E2%84%83%20%E7%96%91%E6%88%90%E5%85%83%E5%87%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n堅定流 無咩巴打反映壞卡好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8840289ac7871f67ffef60e824425804badca6","tid":891113,"uid":130438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e13a999bbce3f39d05d1ae26c7b5c69714fda41","tid":891113,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2200944/20181104_RTX20-1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fc